The table action menu can be added to an action column on a table

TableActionMenu is the component name

It can be added to the actions in a tableDefinition object

TableActionMenu can have a list of menu items
Each menu item declares the jsx and the event code when it is clicked
A menu item also has a visible option and enabled option
Use the bootstrap icon menu-button-wide

Clicking the icon causes the menu to appear
It is a popup menu
The menu is a single-column vertical list of actions


    actions: [
      {
        render: (row) => (
          <button
            className={`${tableStyles.actionButton} ${tableStyles.edit}`}
            onClick={() => handleEdit(row)}
            title="Edit"
          >
            ✏️
          </button>
        ),
      }
    ],


